This is a full-stack expense splitting app (like Splitwise).

Backend: Node.js, Express.js, PostgreSQL (using the `pg` library with a connection pool)
Frontend: React, Tailwind CSS
Auth: JWT tokens stored in localStorage, bcryptjs for password hashing
DB: All queries use raw SQL via pool.query(), no ORM

Conventions:
- Controllers in server/controllers/, routes in server/routes/
- Always use async/await with try/catch
- Always return { success, data, message } shaped responses
- Validate required fields before DB queries
- Never expose passwords in API responses